  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t血雨腥风七四载<br/>\r\n群魔乱舞鬼登台<br/>\r\n万马齐喑人头滚<br/>\r\n菜市口上骨成堆。<br/>\r\n—— 2023.10.1 —— 共匪喋血篡权系列杀人第74年<br/>\r\n百二年来闹共匪<br/>\r\n七四年前匪篡权<br/>\r\n从此杀人日不断<br/>\r\n冤魂怨骨哭到今。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n中共土匪杀人，始自其被俄共捏掐成型之1920年代，只是其1949年在大陆篡权后，更是变本加厉日夜不停，血染江河，尸积山野，可谓中华无不埋白骨寸土，大陆绝不渗鲜血水流。如此嗜杀狂徒，人类历史，横贯东西，前所未有，空前绝后。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n如此喋血屠戮凶残野蛮的<b>共产党系列杀人犯土匪集团</b>，举世凡称其“国家”者，皆杀人帮凶。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9Dd243REhTLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Cwn7DHS.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Cwn7DHS.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Cwn7DHS.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8zN1A1MmVOLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/37P52eN.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/37P52eN.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/37P52eN.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9HRG5FbHIxLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/GDnElr1.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/GDnElr1.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GDnElr1.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS95d2RYakFMLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/ywdXjAL.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ywdXjAL.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ywdXjAL.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
